description: Apple Keyboard The new Apple Keyboard features the compact design of the Apple Wireless Keyboard and the elegant, ultrathin anodized aluminum enclosure and two USB 2.0 ports of the Apple Keyboard with Numeric Keypad. The keyboard has low-profile keys that provide crisp, responsive feel as well asfunction keys for one-touch access to a variety of Mac features such as screen brightness, volume, eject, play/pause, fast-forward and rewind, Expose, and Dashboard. Its compact design fits on your lap or on even the most crowded desk. And two USB 2.0 ports enable you to connect your Mighty Mouse as well as a high-speed peripheral such as a digital camera or printer. Box Contents: Apple Keyboard USB extension cable Printed documentation System Requirements Mac computer with available USB 1.1 or USB 2.0 port Mac OS X v10.5.6or later
title: Apple USB Wired Compact Keyboard MB869LL/A
